{"tid":2079224,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"自彈唱《Rubberband - 睜開眼》","createTime":"2020-06-25T15:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T12:26:51.000Z","uid":18975,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9801d667ee01c8c57e9e49dcb49364c20d6aa272","tid":2079224,"uid":18975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:47:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FpBOF_tZ0gY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFpBOF_tZ0gY&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2Sv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=316d9007\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FpBOF_tZ0gY</a><br />\n<br />\n最鍾意嘅本地學隊<br />\n呢首個真係好代表呢一年嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n斷了的山脊線　鍍了金摩天背面 <br />\n舊老區給拆建　自在遊客買下千噸客船  <br />\n誰在劏開房中幾晚吃不夠吧 <br />\n誰在K房通宵倒了幾多菜渣  <br />\n沒意識　學會了　矇住兩眼　迷信煙花未散<br />\n沒記憶　學會了　矇住耳朵　派對裡任意高歌 <br />\n在這刻　睜開眼　來睜開眼　風光卻失落消散 <br />\n在這刻　若見證　混濁廢氣瀰漫　誰合上眼  <br />\n尚懂得公正　尚靠每雙手拼命 <br />\n做假的不買帳　尚在夏季那夜燭光照樣  <br />\n寧願抽身搬家飛到遠方避世嗎 <br />\n回望那獅子山還是會牽掛 <br />\n若這曲　被禁了　絕唱了　旋律給消滅了　 <br />\n樂器都　弄碎了　全部唱機燒了 也會化做野火燒 <br />\n自這天　睜開眼　睜開眼　時候總不為晚 <br />\n就覺醒　面向這　現實世界無懼　睜開眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1970adf4e2ab481d90b8f36415d1b461eef69a3","tid":2079224,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba45267ccd86d9b6e64912675b666574d0725ef9","tid":2079224,"uid":345289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"巴打你好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/